    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "技能",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">普通攻击</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">物理伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">每回合1次：</span>如果手牌中没有<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">圣俗杂座</span>，则生成手牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">圣俗杂座</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_4511863309173167346.png",
                "id": "talent92298",
                "key": "独舞之邀",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "独舞之邀"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">芙宁娜</span>当前处于「始基力：荒性」形态：召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">沙龙成员</span>。</p><p>（芙宁娜处于「始基力：芒性」形态时，会改为召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">众水的歌者</span>）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/47e3b8a03c0e9406c19655e1aa7c3b30_7761296370498351053.png",
                "id": "talent54807",
                "key": "孤心沙龙",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "孤心沙龙"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素伤害</span>，生成<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">普世欢腾</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/e5d9f5e8170236ccfb246be6a8bee57f_6971777398447276612.png",
                "id": "talent51237",
                "key": "万众狂欢",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "万众狂欢"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">被动技能</span></p><p>【被动】战斗开始时，生成手牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">圣俗杂座</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/be37947534ecad684025e9577469afa4_8149885978265147508.png",
                "id": "talent2804",
                "key": "始基力：圣俗杂座",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "始基力：圣俗杂座"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">事件牌</span></p><p>在「始基力：荒性」和「始基力：芒性」之中，切换芙宁娜的形态。</p><p>如果我方场上存在<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">沙龙成员</span>或<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">众水的歌者</span>，也切换其形态。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1210668648965550886.png",
                "id": "talent98824",
                "key": "圣俗杂座",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/b4812801014e3b4dfaed86c27639933c_3153270760010769574.png",
                "title": "圣俗杂座"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>造成1点<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素伤害</span>。如果我方存在生命值至少为6的角色，则对一位受伤最少的我方角色造成1点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">穿透伤害</span>，然后再造成1点<span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">水元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：2</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到4次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1172284487384045779.png",
                "id": "talent74924",
                "key": "沙龙成员",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/742ece024b8fa2d5c64bdb5a98710fb7_7580222378922701899.png",
                "title": "沙龙成员"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">召喚物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>治疗所有我方角色1点。如果我方存在生命值不多于5的角色，则再治疗一位受伤最多的角色1点。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">可用次数：2</span>（可叠加，最多叠加到4次）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_1137768128784034776.png",
                "id": "talent31173",
                "key": " 众水的歌者",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/d87cb48ac9ce6214f901cfb7aa5cc542_8015282616683357498.png",
                "title": " 众水的歌者"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害<span>+2</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害<span>+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害<span>+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</span></p><p><span>【</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span><span>+</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span><span>】</span><span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害<span>+1，生成使下次火/雷伤害+2的[</span><span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span><span>]</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">出战状态</span></p><p><span>我方对敌方出战角色造成</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素伤害</span>或<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素伤害</span>时，伤害值<span>+2。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: white\">可用次数：1</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_2400666858435690645.png",
                "id": "talent55210",
                "key": "水元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">穿透伤害</span></strong></p><p>穿透伤害无法受到伤害加成，但是也无法被护盾、伤害免疫等效果抵消。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">狂欢值</span></strong></p><p>我方造成的伤害+1。（包括角色引发的扩散伤害）</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：1</span>（可叠加，没有上限）</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span></strong></p><p>每回合结束阶段，<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>-1；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><br><br></span><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">普世欢腾</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">我方出战角色受到伤害或治疗后：</span>叠加1点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">狂欢值</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">持续回合：2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/14/157749474/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_8886572353548015211.png",
